      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted (2.1M, 5.4M, 11.8M elements). GCI for relative hemolysis index is 2.3%, well below 5% threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
